obj_root_law:
  slug the-government-of-union-territories-act-1963
  handle (1546)
  collectionHandle 123456789/1362
  title `The Government of Union Territories Act, 1963`
  actNumber (20)
  enactmentDate 1963-05-10
  sourceUrl `https://www.indiacode.nic.in/handle/123456789/1546`
  sources obj_root_law_sources
  sections obj_root_law_sections
  hindiTitle `संघ राज्‍यक्षेत्र शासन अधिनियम, 1963`
  actYear (1963)
  ministry `Ministry of Home Affairs`
  department `Department of States`
  longTitle `An Act to provide for Legislative Assemblies and Councils of Ministers for certain Union territories and for certain other matters.`
  enforcementDate 13-05-1963
  notification `13-5-1963, vide notification No. G.S.R. 814, dated 13-5-1963, in respect of Part I, sections 3, 4 and 14 of Part II, Part III, sections 53, 56 and 57 of Part V and First and Second Schedules as applicable to the Union territory of Goa, Daman and Diu, see Gazette of India, Extraordinary, Part II, Section 3(i). 20-12-1963, vide notification. No. G.S.R 1922, dated 16-12-1963, in respect of remaining provisions of the Act applicable to the Union territory of Goa, Daman and Diu, see Gazette of India, Extraordinary, Part II, Section 3(i). 17-2-1972, vide notification No. G.S.R. 81(E), dated 16-2-1972, in respect of sections 1, 2, 3, 4, 14, 38, 43A and 56 of the Act shall come into force in the Union territory of Mizoram, see Gazette of India, Extraordinary, Part II, Section 3(i). 3-5-1972, vide notification No. G.S.R. 269(E), dated 30-4-1972, in respect of all the provisions of the Act, other than those which have already come into force in the Union territory of Mizoram, shall, so far as they are applicable, come into force in that Union territory, see Gazette of India, Extraordinary, Part II, Section 3(i). 13-5-1963, vide notification. No. G.S.R. 815, dated 13-5-1963, in respect of Part I, sections 53, 56 and 57 of Part V and the Second Schedule in the Union territory of Pondicherry, see Gazette of India, Extraordinary, Part II, Section 3(i). 1-7-1963, vide notification No. G.S.R. 1025, dated 15-6-1963, for the remaining provisions came into force in the Union territory of Pondicherry, see Gazette of India, Extraordinary, Part II, Section 3(i). 1-7-1963, vide notification No. S.O. 1660, dated 14-6-1963, in respect of all the provisions in the Union territories of Himachal Pradesh, Manipur and Tripura, and so much of the provisions as apply to the Union territory of Delhi, see Gazette of India, Extraordinary, Part II, Section 3(ii). 1-7-1963, vide notification No. G.S.R. 1025, dated 15-6-1963, in respect of the provisions as apply to the Union territory of Dadra and Nagar Haveli, see Gazette of India, Extraordinary, Part II, Section 3(i).`
  fetchedAt `2026-05-09T10:22:08.095Z`
  translations obj_root_law_translations
